---
import GlobalLayout from '../layouts/GlobalLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/game/PageHeader.astro';
---

<GlobalLayout title="About" description="Learn about Mochileaf — a cozy gaming content platform built for calm, beautiful play.">
  <PageHeader
    badge="Our story"
    title="A sanctuary for cozy gamers"
    description="Mochileaf was born from a love of games that feel like a warm cup of tea — peaceful, visual, and full of heart."
  />
  <article class="page-container-below-header max-w-3xl prose-cozy">
    <p>
      We believe gaming content can be editorial, elegant, and calming. No neon overload, no aggressive
      esports energy — just thoughtful guides, gentle tier lists, and stories that honor the worlds you love.
    </p>
    <p>
      Each game on Mochileaf gets its own dedicated hub with characters, builds, news, and guides — all
      wrapped in a consistent design system inspired by soft fantasy and anime-inspired interfaces.
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-primary mt-10">Built for growth</h2>
    <p>
      This MVP is structured for future API integration, AdSense placement, and multi-game expansion.
      Add a game to <code class="text-sage-500">src/data/games.ts</code>, create routes under
      <code class="text-sage-500">src/pages/[game]/</code>, and your hub is ready.
    </p>
  </article>
</GlobalLayout>
